org.hibernate.ogm.dialect.query.spi

Class QueryParameters

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hibernate.ogm.dialect.query.spi.QueryParameters

  • public class QueryParameters
extends Object
    Represents the parameters passed to a query. Modelled after QueryParameters in Hibernate ORM, providing only those values needed for OGM's purposes at this point.
    Author:
    Gunnar Morling
